WGCNA gene expression data for wgcna_analysis.

Source: R/wgcna_gene_exp.R
wgcna_gene_exp.Rd

WGCNA gene expression data for wgcna_analysis.

Usage

data(wgcna_gene_exp)

Format

Dataframe: include gene expression data.

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/WGCNA/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example data
data(wgcna_gene_exp)

# 3. View example data
wgcna_gene_exp
